com.pse.testserver.entities

Class Category

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pse.testserver.entities.Category

  • @Entity
public class Category
extends java.lang.Object
    Entity class for the persisted category data from the "categories" table. Represents a category, providing access to the category's unique id, name, subcategories, groups and events.
